      "rationale": "Input uncertainty characterization was limited to flow rate and viscosity. Sobol sensitivity analysis was not performed. Remaining input parameters treated as deterministic. Epistemic gap."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Test samples",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 5,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental sample size justified by statistical power analysis; inter-laboratory reproducibility demonstrated.",
      "rationale": "FDA benchmark dataset uses a fixed sample of experiments without formal power analysis or inter-laboratory reproducibility study. Epistemic gap at MRL 5."
    },
    {
