      "acceptanceCriteria": "Formal mapping between simulation input parameters and experimental conditions documented with equivalency justification for all non-identical parameters.",
      "rationale": "Equivalency between simulation boundary conditions and experimental test conditions was not formally documented beyond informal engineering judgment. Epistemic gap."
