    "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/decision/dr-vad-hemolysis-cou2-minimal-001",
    "type": "DecisionRecord",
    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Under the Minimal profile declaration, the seven assessed credibility factors collectively demonstrate sufficient evidence to support conditional acceptance of the CFD hemolysis model for the described VAD application. The six not-assessed factors represent acknowledged epistemic gaps that are documented for future resolution. The assessment team accepts the model for continued use in clinical research support activities with the understanding that MRL 5 full compliance requires resolution of the outstanding gaps prior to regulatory submission.",
